TITLE: Episode 114 - The Remnant Remains, w/ RemnantMD
DESCRIPTION: Thankfully it does remain, the remnant among us are out there, and in the medical field as well. This past week we caught up with neuroradiologist, RemnantMD and talked about confounding, conflict in the workplace, and covid communism generally.
